  <description>
    Flyby F-11 quadcopter with ISR (Intelligence, Surveillance, Reconnaissance) camera payload.

    Platform Specifications:
    - Base mass: 4.5 kg
    - Payload mass: 1.8 kg (Sony A7R + Gremsy T3V3 gimbal)
    - Total mass: 6.3 kg
    - Arm span: 550 mm (motor-to-motor)

    Payload Specifications:
    - Camera: Sony A7R (36 MP full-frame)
    - Gimbal: Gremsy T3V3 (3-axis stabilization)
    - Pan: +/-345 degrees
    - Tilt: +/-120 degrees
    - Roll: +/-45 degrees

    Features:
    - High-resolution RGB camera sensor
    - 3-axis stabilized gimbal
    - IMU and GPS sensors
    - ArduPilot SITL integration
  </description>
